{"tid":527824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"文件揭美斯年賺1億歐元","createTime":"2018-01-13T05:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T17:12:47.000Z","uid":132262,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c8981cbcf8080865f72d7f4959d1b4df09609395","tid":527824,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LP8yUVPm7W3rfFmF2OgoJpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ee179bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】最近有一份文件流出，披露了球王美斯原來每年在球會的收入高達1億歐元。<br />\n<br />\n30歲的阿根廷球星美斯（Lionel Messi）今季跟巴塞隆拿續約至2021年，根據法國調查網站Mediapart獲得的文件所顯示，他在球會未來4季的薪金高達7100萬歐元，加上15%肖像權收入，以及約滿前不離隊的7000萬歐元金額，即合共賺取4.175億歐元。 這比皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度及去夏以破世界紀錄轉會費投巴黎聖日耳門的尼馬都要多。 除此之外，這名阿根廷球王的合約中還有多項獎金條款，要是出戰60%比賽，會有190萬歐元、要是巴塞贏得歐聯冠軍，更會有1200萬歐元，認真和味。不過，分析指這份天價合約成功留下美斯，卻嚴重破壞了球會的薪金系統。"},{"pid":"5ce9f8d7a32803ec0e0ebfafdff66513f7de26ce","tid":527824,"uid":1139,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27048e4b382aefc94c41b25c22034070889cefd6","tid":527824,"uid":1734,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"真係值 場場交足功課 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 40歲都咁勁你都照比嫁啦"},{"pid":"395bc4e019bcc80769c61d83dd694478befda08a","tid":527824,"uid":120990,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"我朗值幾多億??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86902bde5bc668d0c3a929dd1fdea05df555317","tid":527824,"uid":20896,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"幾年前就值"},{"pid":"163030836696f3c7f380fa337967fa4a7e61f88f","tid":527824,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:00:08.000Z","msg":"話咁快..美斯30歲啦.."},{"pid":"3a7eaa43